{"tid":1062660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新西蘭恐襲：槍手表明支持 PewDiePie稱極嘔心","createTime":"2019-03-15T08:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T18:01:14.000Z","uid":119223,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b62c5d84ee339b16e8d896f0a332ec13b747b70d","tid":1062660,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T08:50:00.000Z","msg":"新西蘭基督城周五（15日）發生清真寺連環恐襲後，其中一名白人槍手上載打機式擎槍殺人片段，並在影片中表明支持打機網紅PewDiePie。PewDiePie在twitter上回應指，對於槍手說出自己的名字，感到很嘔心，並向受害人致哀。 <br />\n<br />\n來自澳洲的白人槍手塔蘭特上載第一身殺人過程，畫面仿如槍擊遊戲。他又在影片中，叫網民訂閱PewDiePie的打機內容。PewDiePie發聲明表示：「剛得知新西蘭基督城的可怕消息，這人口中吐出我的名字，令我感到極度嘔心。我的心與受害人、家屬及所有受影響人士同在。」新西蘭警方及澳洲在野黨領袖肖特，均呼籲民眾不要再傳播影片。 <br />\n<br />\nPewDiePie原名謝爾貝里，來自瑞典，其Youtube有近9千萬人訂閱，前年年收入9千多萬美元，曾登上最賺錢的打機網紅首位。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190315/photo/bkn-20190315131424907-0315_00912_001_01p.jpg?20190315152652\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190315%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190315131424907-0315_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20190315152652&h=975cfaab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190315/mobile/bkn-20190315131424907-0315_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190315%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190315131424907-0315_00912_001.html&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsacg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=163e7cc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190315/mobile/bkn-20190315131424907-0315_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9eae40930b765fff706dce99e959e94103ab79e7","tid":1062660,"uid":119223,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T08:51:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=PTVBGmOQFT0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPTVBGmOQFT0&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsacg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=15bc8113\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=PTVBGmOQFT0</a><br />\n<br />\n條友寫到1999 係到補充更正下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為近年youtube既第一位sub大戰，而帶起一種網絡meme文化 pewdiepie vs t series<br />\n<br />\n所以先會不時出現sub to pewdiepie呢句口號<br />\n<br />\n另外pewdiepie一早轉型冇打機好耐"},{"pid":"e4eefb90d4811394f8af560b9e7058e4edb84b1c","tid":1062660,"uid":119223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d9dc4bccf03fc7e3b8b0e52b4702c9b3ed98c5","tid":1062660,"uid":81698,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"陰公pewdiepie又比人擺上台<br />\n一陣又比人挖返佢叫非洲細路跳舞單野出黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14cead66ceb6736771a137f3d167d899dda57f59","tid":1062660,"uid":2404,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:15:04.000Z","msg":"句野同阿彌陀佛一樣，都係口號嚟啫"},{"pid":"868a629268f62c2b4dc2a6aacf9695c9a9fdf97b","tid":1062660,"uid":26752,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"Wsj又有野寫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9bd575f05ecf2446e32e0fed9cf4d1d6acd887","tid":1062660,"uid":6530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:45:07.000Z","msg":"今次仆硬街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早彈出嚟澄清都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4785643da7ab40f8d78327f00c3f0b3bba4b69e","tid":1062660,"uid":51753,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09